description
Prometheus-Praxis integrated execution fabric for planetary stewardship.
Implements six pillars from Architecting Authority: Eco-Work, Psychological
Continuity, Smart-City Infrastructure, Cybernetics & Augmented Citizens,
Advanced Healthcare, Sovereign Governance. Extends into Cosmic Stewardship.
Source grounding:
 - Cognitive City OS: https://www.pwc.com/m1/en/publications/2025/docs/cognitive-city-operating-system-future-cities.pdf
 - EU Nature Restoration Regulation: https://environment.ec.europa.eu/topics/nature-and-biodiversity/nature-restoration-regulation_en
 - UN Decade on Ecosystem Restoration: https://www.decadeonrestoration.org/
 - ISO/IEC 42001: https://www.iso.org/standard/42001
 - NIST AI RMF: https://www.nist.gov/itl/ai-risk-management-framework
 - FDA Breakthrough Devices: https://www.fda.gov/medical-devices/how-study-and-market-your-device/breakthrough-devices-program
end-description

